<% content_for :title, "NW5k Phnom Penh - free, weekly 5k walk/run" %>
<div class="w-4/5 md:w-3/4 lg:w-2/3 xl:w-1/2 mx-auto py-8">
	<div class="justify-center items-center bg-white mx-auto rounded-lg p-4 lg:p-16">
		<h1 class="text-center text-6xl font-bold text-purple-600 transition duration-500">New World 5k</h1>
		<p class="py-2">New World 5k is a free, fun and friendly social event. Walk, jog, run or just have a chat. All ages and abiliites are welcome!</p>
		<h2 class="font-bold text-purple-600">When?</h2>
		<p class="py-2">It's on every Saturday at 7:00am</p>
		<h2 class="font-bold text-purple-600">Where?</h2>
		<p class="py-2">Meet at the park inside Borey New World, Wat Samroung Andet (Phnom Penh, Cambodia). See the <%= link_to "Course Page", course_path %> for more details.</p>
		<h2 class="font-bold text-purple-600">Is it timed? Is it a race?</h2>
		<p class="py-2">The event is timed and results are recorded. See the <%= link_to "Results Page", results_path %> for previous results.</p>
		<p class="py-2">...but it's not a race. There are no prizes for first, just a big congratulations if you improve on your best time.</p>
		<h2 class="font-bold text-purple-600">Is this a parkrun?</h2>
		<p class="py-2">No, we love parkrun® and we'd love to see it come to Cambodia but this is not an official parkrun® event! On the other hand, yes, the format of this event is heavily inspired by parkun®.</p>
	</div>
</div>
